      <div class="tab-content px-2" id="v-pills-tabContent">
        <div class="tab-pane tab-text tab-text1 fade show active" id="v-pills-1" role="tabpanel"
          aria-labelledby="v-pills-1-tab">
          <div class="row align-items-center">
            <div class="col-lg-6">
              <h3>Attain and Retain the Best Talent</h3>
              <p>Push your HR process from easy job posting, evaluating, and hiring the right person to the development
                phase, and smoothly manage the breeze-away recruitment life cycle. </p>
              <p>StaffViz offers a centralized hub to coordinate all things HR management - develop your workforce so
                that every individual expends energy in the right direction.</p>
              <ul>
                <li>Define shifts, manage breaks, and analyze performance trends</li>
                <li>Build a happier workplace with fully maintained workforce</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6 d-lg-block d-none">
              <img src="{{asset('/public/assets/img/Group1707488067.webp')}}" alt="HR">
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
        <div class="tab-pane tab-text tab-text2 fade" id="v-pills-2" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="v-pills-2-tab">
          <div class="row align-items-center">
            <div class="col-lg-6">
              <h3>Help them Stay One-Step Ahead </h3>
              <p>Make articles and quizzes to keep your resources up to date regarding changing industry scenarios,
                technology trends, and dynamic clients' demands.</p>
              <p>StaffViz gives the freedom to set broader goals and visualize bigger ideas with a high-performing
                workforce. Schedule courses and assign articles to bring employees to par with the growth curve.</p>
              <ul>
                <li>Get in-depth visibility of team's productivity and performance</li>
                <li>Improve employee performance with detailed analysis & visibility</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6 d-lg-block d-none">
              <img src="{{asset('/public/assets/img/02-Training Management.webp')}}" alt="Onboarding-&-Trainings">
            </div>
